    <DisplayName>Sqlx IntelliSense Extension</DisplayName>
    <Description xml:space="preserve">🚀 Enhanced Visual Studio IntelliSense support for Sqlx - High-performance .NET ORM with source generators.

Features:
• 🔍 SQL syntax highlighting in [Sqlx] attributes
• 💡 IntelliSense for table names and column names
• ⚡ Real-time SQL validation and error detection
• 🎯 Smart code completion for database operations
• 🛡️ Type-safe parameter suggestions
• 📊 Multi-database dialect support (MySQL, SQL Server, PostgreSQL, Oracle, DB2, SQLite)
• 🔧 Repository pattern scaffolding
• 📈 Performance hints and optimization suggestions

Transform your data access experience with intelligent SQL assistance!</Description>
